Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:36.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最愛之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:41.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就是永遠在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:49.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}讓我心滿意足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:01.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但卻難以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:11.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然會感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:16.79,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仍然相信命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:22.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}天空的航跡雲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:28.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}擦過天邊的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:36.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只願送達昔日的淡淡思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:45.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:49.01,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界彷如閃耀的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:54.21,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}伴著心動的春風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:59.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻  好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:03.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:08.78,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但卻難以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:18.57,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只願守望你
