Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome  暑假！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,60)\1c4B33D1\3c000000\bord3\fad(200,0)}剩餘\N41天
