Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽  我現在出門買遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來四十天人間蒸發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但請您不要擔心  就這樣  拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手  我的一千小時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  跟客人打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬還記得吧  以前住我們隔壁的鮎川一家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬十年沒見了  還記得我這個阿姨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太記得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理快看  是桂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理  都說是桂馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰…來著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打遊戲打遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  這幾天都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地獄開報告會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一點玩遊戲的時間都不給嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給哥哥大人帶的特產  針球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有妹妹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾露希  您好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個玩具真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起  我家的孩子還是這麼不禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}完全沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}…也許有點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  桂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說不記得  太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  小學一年級時你倆不是同班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都只拍到了半身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  印象中是有個扭扭捏捏的女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的記憶真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種場合就算忘記了也得說記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題毫不重要  我要去買遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八月底再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的教育果然有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛探測器好像響了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十天  一千小時！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測器響了就有申告的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免兩個惡魔同時追捕同一對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  暑假  你比任何女主角都更有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定驅魂跑進哥哥大人的青梅竹馬身體裡去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  竟敢妄稱青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0\fad(120,0)}Flag  壹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  貳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  肆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fs20\bord0}Flag  伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長期構建哥哥或弟弟這種戀人以下的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定過通往結局的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回憶中將要忘記一切的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換了截然不同的立場再會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才叫青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  那種似有似無的女人不是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  遊戲裡的青梅竹馬可是未來的結婚對象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要隨便地設定這麼重要的關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是神哥哥大人忘記了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都幹了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  起碼先道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能捫心自問一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是抱著何等的決心踏進桂木家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你卻一句「不記得」一筆帶過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這更傷人的話語了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒指望過你能幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助？幫助是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不響了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驅魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟諾拉小姐為敵是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追到這麼遠的地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條大魚可不能放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是明明白白地登記了負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  接下來就輪到我們出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬體內有驅魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說那不是青梅竹馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就申請負責了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要我出馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這套路挺常見應該不難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是內向女孩的強烈願望化為別的人格表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒指望過你能幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞島學園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的變化最大  跟十年前相比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上高中就別老是按泡沫包裝紙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別  別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好擔心天理的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄安娜  為什麼要把他推下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以創造和他對話的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天理在抵抗才顯得這麼奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你要我馬上說出口我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理  我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在被人追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的我能力不夠  必須要依靠他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能信任桂木桂馬那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他簡直就是鈍感的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為桂馬同學一定能幫助我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理的驅魂負責人被搶先登記了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責人是…諾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在我的負責地區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  有其他人幫我解決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  諾拉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再和桂木桂馬說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將思緒投入波浪之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能獲得一時的安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你心靈的間隙  還是會一直殘留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心靈的間隙  就由我來填補吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切都交給我吧  來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就聽聽他說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟醫生問診差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮  繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這些人就是狄安娜所說的… 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我們是你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中現在住著一個叫驅魂的壞東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管就會越來越強釀成大禍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要把他給淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將產生間隙的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用數倍的巨大慾望來填補的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅魂就會滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一萬元的人就給他一百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要戀人的女性就給他男公關部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受欺凌的人就給他復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的羽衣能夠反映出人心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就簡單了  喜歡和討厭的二選一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就讓這個男人吃點苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉  她不是兩方面都說NO了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界憎恨比愛要來得更多更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都當成憎恨的話一般都沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒有聽她細細道來的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  不愧是諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我可以殺了他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉以快速解決聞名  試過半天內就趕出了驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  失敗次數也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還試過反過頭來把驅魂養大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還試過拋下協力者  自己一個人趕出驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這做法實際上是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這都是傳聞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已經和我無關…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底什麼地方得罪你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著  通往光明未來的招待券哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公開處刑通知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心靈的間隙由我們來填補
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在海邊公園  等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲  遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥我要被綁著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次好像也能快速解決呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  還挺快的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹睜大眼睛看著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就讓你憎恨的男人吃點苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不恨桂馬同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃描器可不是這麼說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個男人你的心靈才會產生間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個間隙裡面就躲著驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉  請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是我的協力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣  這傢伙就是諾拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更有蹂躪的價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔復活後再收服可是禁止的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原則上禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是絕對禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的協力者還不太成氣候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是沒辦法才這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我要讓他比死更難受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這個男人最重要的東西給毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  你要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學  我好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹  真的是小四妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於  來到結局的彼岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼願望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非這就是那傢伙所喜歡的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把你最重要的東西給毀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學是怎麼看我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼問  說不出口啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肯說的話  我也說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂…桂…桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎樣  失去至愛的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀取讀取讀取讀取讀取…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰  到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死小四妹的到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了煽情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者製造膚淺的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不動就把女主角殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有想過被你們殺掉的女主角是什麼感受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把  小四妹還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心  好噁心  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  天理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人漂亮地把那兩人趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓這個人來保護我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那種  像那種噁心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有活著的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊  諾拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是協力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭檔的惡魔也會一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希也會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死就死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要碰上這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話能躲起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是被發現了就沒地方可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是需要解決根本問題的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  為啥非得要我保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這樣放著不管會很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉認為只要讓哥哥大人吃苦頭驅魂就會跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用別的驅魂來當作天理的驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓其被諾拉抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後被發現了也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把我被她盯上的這個狀態給解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我沒有能替換的驅魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過白亞可能有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我悠閒玩遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個狀況了還能這麼冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早知道會有這種事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就多帶幾個備用電池出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前好像也在哪裡發生過類似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就剩下兩個人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是那種氣氛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出一點勇氣  天理這種時候就該…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這次逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你身上還留著驅魂那還是什麼都沒解決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要依靠驅魂  自己想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅魂什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好像天理有問題似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能原諒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅魂就給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要依靠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我之間有什麼聯繫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也說了不記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…從來都沒有忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬同學  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明都不是這裡的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面的路你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我以前來過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和桂馬同學一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候也擔心過電池的問題
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬頭看看吧  夜空的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顆星星和那顆星星和那顆星星連接在一起就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galge座了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那旁邊的是美少女遊戲座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再旁邊的就是戀愛模擬遊戲座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來很像但全部都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部連在一起成了消防車
